headline: State Street's Paglia on PRIV SEC Concerns, Lack of Inflows
summary: State Street Corp. and Apollo Global Management Inc.'s hotly anticipated private credit exchange-traded fund has been met with muted demand so far from investors and concerns from the SEC. State Street Global Advisors Chief Business Officer Anna Paglia has more on the story.
